the three godfathers is a 1948 american western film directed by john ford and written by peter b. kyne . the film stars john wayne , harry carey , harry carey jr. , harry carey , harry carey jr. , harry carey jr. , harry carey jr. , harry carey , harry carey , harry carey jr. , harry carey , harry carey , harry carey , harry carey , and harry carey . the film was released by warner bros. on december 13 , 1948 . the film was directed by john ford and was based on a novel by peter b. kyne .